STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Seith KEITH, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-1413 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Seith Keith appeals his convictions for robbery in the first degree and willful injury resulting in bodily injury. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
